column1:
[Mandatory]
Choose action required for the product item. 
- Add New Item
- Edit Item Content Info
- Delete The SKU
- Change Price Only
- Change Active Status Only
column2:
[Mandatory]
State the SKU Code that is used by vendor to track the product item in their Inventory Management.
column3:
[Mandatory]
Except for Fresh Produce (Vegetable, Fruit, Flower, Meat and Seafood) and Bakery Good (Baked Bread and Cake). 
If need exemption, then please submit Exemption Request at: https://forms.gle/1C9z8Znf4EkcdKG27

Example of Barcode:
column4:
[Mandatory]
The Product Title of each product item must be unique; if there is same Product Title for 2 or more product items, then it will be omitted.
Product Title should follow below format:
[Brand] [Product name] [Quantity (if any)] [Weight / Volume]
- Tiger Lager Beer Can 10s x 320ml
- Blackmores Men’s Performance Multivitamin 100 Tablets
column5:
[Optional]
The Product Title of each product item must be unique; if there is same Product Title for 2 or more product items, then it will be omitted.
Product Title should follow below format:

- Blackmores Men’s Performance Multivitamin 100 Tablets
column6:

Product Title should follow below format:

column7:
[Mandatory]
Fill in "Unknown Brand" if the product item is handmade or have no Brand info provided.
column8:
[Mandatory]
Fill in "Unknown Principal" if the product item have no Manufacturer info provided.
column9:
[Mandatory]
Input the link of Google Drive folder that store all the product images at here.
column10:
[Mandatory]
Input number only and can up to 2 decimal points. 
E.g. 10.50
column11:
[Mandatory]
Put "0" if there is no limit per checkout.
E.g. If you only allow customers to buy 3 items of that product per order, then put "3" for that product item.
column12:
[Mandatory]
Choose the most suitable category from the dropbox.
Please see "Category Tree" tab for the full list of categories.
column13:
[Mandatory]
- 0 = the product is Inactive and not showing in App and Web
- 1 = the product is Active and showing in App and Web
column14:
[Optional]
Choose the Tagging that matched your product item for Disclaimer purpose. 
- disclaimer_baby_formula
- disclaimer_adult_product
- disclaimer_pharmacy
- disclaimer_alcoholic
- disclaimer_tobacco
column15:
[Optional]
- Only accept text, no image and video is allowed. 
- No word formatting is allowed (e.g. Bold, Italic, Underline, etc). 
- Paragraphing (breaking the description into multiple lines) is allowed. 
- Special character is allowed (e.g. ! @ # $ % ^ & *) but the file needs to be saved in “CSV UTF-8” format to maintain the special character. 
- Maximum 8400 characters limit including spaces.
